309192699.text: "Furthermore, we provide mechanistic evidences that most of the miR-130b-dependent effects are due to PPARgamma suppression that in turn deregulates PTEN, E-cadherin, Snail, and vascular endothelial growth factor, key mediators of cell proliferation, EMT, and angiogenesis."
